{"lemma":"خِتانِ","slug":"خِتانِ","root":"خ.ت.ن","root_slug":"خ-ت-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ت-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10025"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%90%D8%AA%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"circumcision"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/xi.taːn/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10025","headword_ar":"خِتَانٌ","root":"xtn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Circumcision,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a boy, (S, * Mgh, * Msb, * K, TA,) and of a girl; (TA;) a subst. from 1 in the first of the senses explained above; (S, Mgh, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xitaAnapN","text_ar":"خِتَانَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, K.) You say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uToHirato xitaAnatuhu","text_ar":"اُطْحِرَتْ خِتَانَتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His circumcision was made to be extirpative."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A feast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"banquet, to which people are invited on account of a circumcision."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kunotu fiY xitaAni fulaAnK","text_ar":"كُنْتُ فِى خِتَانِ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I was at the feast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"banquet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  See also 1, third sentence. ―         -b4-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part, of the male, which is the place of circumcision;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, Mgh, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the female"},{"kind":"text","text":"likewise; (T, Mgh, TA;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part, of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroj","text_ar":"فَرْج"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is the place of circumcision."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) Hence, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA A@lotaqaY","text_ar":"اـِذَا ا@لْتَقَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxitaAnaAni","text_ar":"الخِتَانَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When the two places of circumcision meet together"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, * Msb, * TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AilotiqaA='u AlxitaAnayoni","text_ar":"اِلْتِقَا=ءُ الخِتَانَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a euphemism, metonymically denoting the disappearing, or causing to disappear, of the part of the penis that is above, or beyond, the place of circumcision (Mgh, * Msb, TA) in the vulva of the woman. (Mgh, * TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}